    "skillPath3": {
      "pathName": "The Improviser",
      "skill1": {
        "skillName": "Augmentation",
        "stat": "cra",
        "definition": "<p>A Craftsman can make an Augmentation roll at a DC listed in the Augmentation chart to augment a weapon or Armor with their crafting tools. This augmentation takes 3 rounds. While a forge isn&rsquo;t required, it grants a +2 to the roll. A fumble results in the item taking damage equal to the fumble value.</p>\n<p><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><strong>Weapons</strong></span></p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Reinforced:</strong>&nbsp;<br><strong>DC</strong> 14<br>+2 Reliablity</li>\n<li><strong>Serration/Spikes</strong><strong><br></strong>DC 16<br>+25% Bleed</li>\n<li><strong>Lighten</strong><strong><br></strong><strong>DC</strong> 18<br>+1 Weapon Accuracy</li>\n</ul>\n<p><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><strong>Armor</strong></span></p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Reinforced<br>DC</strong> 14<br>+2 SP</li>\n<li><strong>Camouflage<br></strong><strong>DC</strong> 16<br>+1 Stealth</li>\n<li><strong>Studded<br></strong><strong>DC</strong> 18<br>2 Damage to grapplers</li>\n</ul>",
